  ('SCIENCE-G1-SFI-SCO1', 'SCIENCE-G1-SFI-ELO1', 'SCIENCE-G1-SFI', 'SCIENCE', 'science', 'G1', '1', 'Structure, Function and Information Processing', 'Define the terms: •	Mimic/mimicking
•	Protection
