•	Defence
•	Camouflage
•	Grow
•	Nutrients
•	Predators', 389, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:21.83026+00:00'),
  ('SCIENCE-G1-SFI-SCO2', 'SCIENCE-G1-SFI-ELO1', 'SCIENCE-G1-SFI', 'SCIENCE', 'science', 'G1', '1', 'Structure, Function and Information Processing', 'Name and describe some living and non-living things in the environment', 390, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:21.83026+00:00'),
