  ('SS-G1-HCT-SCO1', 'SS-G1-HCT-ELO1', 'SS-G1-HCT', 'SS', 'social-studies', 'G1', '1', 'Historical and Cultural Thinking', 'K - State different forms of celebrations that are practiced in families to build pride and identity. ', 459, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:21.83026+00:00'),
  ('SS-G1-HCT-SCO2', 'SS-G1-HCT-ELO1', 'SS-G1-HCT', 'SS', 'social-studies', 'G1', '1', 'Historical and Cultural Thinking', 'K - Identify aspects of culture such as food, music, dance that are relevant to celebrations in families. ', 460, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:21.83026+00:00'),
  ('SS-G1-HCT-SCO3', 'SS-G1-HCT-ELO1', 'SS-G1-HCT', 'SS', 'social-studies', 'G1', '1', 'Historical and Cultural Thinking', 'S - Demonstrate different forms of celebration in the family and explain the importance of preserving local culture. ', 461, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:21.83026+00:00'),
  ('SS-G1-HCT-SCO4', 'SS-G1-HCT-ELO1', 'SS-G1-HCT', 'SS', 'social-studies', 'G1', '1', 'Historical and Cultural Thinking', 'V- Appreciate their cultural heritage ', 462, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:21.83026+00:00'),
  ('SS-G1-HCT-SCO5', 'SS-G1-HCT-ELO1', 'SS-G1-HCT', 'SS', 'social-studies', 'G1', '1', 'Historical and Cultural Thinking', 'K - List religious and national festivals celebrated by the family. ', 463, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:21.83026+00:00'),
  ('SS-G1-HCT-SCO6', 'SS-G1-HCT-ELO1', 'SS-G1-HCT', 'SS', 'social-studies', 'G1', '1', 'Historical and Cultural Thinking', 'S - Investigate and report how the family, school and nation celebrate various religious and national festivals.', 464, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:21.83026+00:00'),
  ('SS-G1-HCT-SCO7', 'SS-G1-HCT-ELO1', 'SS-G1-HCT', 'SS', 'social-studies', 'G1', '1', 'Historical and Cultural Thinking', 'V - Respect that families celebrate religious and national festivals in different ways, and that the families may choose not to celebrate some or all of these occasions. ', 465, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:21.83026+00:00'),
  ('SS-G1-HCT-SCO8', 'SS-G1-HCT-ELO1', 'SS-G1-HCT', 'SS', 'social-studies', 'G1', '1', 'Historical and Cultural Thinking', 'K - Identify the national symbols of their country.  ', 466, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:21.83026+00:00'),
  ('SS-G1-HCT-SCO9', 'SS-G1-HCT-ELO1', 'SS-G1-HCT', 'SS', 'social-studies', 'G1', '1', 'Historical and Cultural Thinking', 'S - Describe the national symbols through drawing, painting and /or other expressions.  ', 467, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:21.83026+00:00'),
  ('SS-G1-HCT-SCO10', 'SS-G1-HCT-ELO1', 'SS-G1-HCT', 'SS', 'social-studies', 'G1', '1', 'Historical and Cultural Thinking', 'V- Appreciate that their national symbols are unique and special to their country and should be respected.', 468, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:21.83026+00:00'),
  ('SS-G1-CP-SCO1', 'SS-G1-CP-ELO1', 'SS-G1-CP', 'SS', 'social-studies', 'G1', '1', 'Civic Particpation', 'K-Understand the importance of keeping their home, school, and community tidy and clean. ', 469, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:21.83026+00:00'),
  ('SS-G1-CP-SCO2', 'SS-G1-CP-ELO1', 'SS-G1-CP', 'SS', 'social-studies', 'G1', '1', 'Civic Particpation', 'S- Practice putting garbage and litter in trash cans at school and home.  ', 470, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:21.83026+00:00'),
  ('SS-G1-CP-SCO3', 'SS-G1-CP-ELO1', 'SS-G1-CP', 'SS', 'social-studies', 'G1', '1', 'Civic Particpation', 'V-Observe and appreciate places in their environment that are kept clean and tidy.', 471, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:21.83026+00:00'),
