•	Organic materials', 1123, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:22.85096+00:00'),
  ('SCIENCE-G2-ES-SCO57', 'SCIENCE-G2-ES-ELO3', 'SCIENCE-G2-ES', 'SCIENCE', 'science', 'G2', '2', 'Earth Systems', 'Define and identify locations of different landforms and bodies of water in the Caribbean region, such as hills, rivers, mountains, canyons, oceans, islands, volcanoes, deserts, waterfalls, and estuaries.', 1124, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:22.85096+00:00'),
