  ('SCIENCE-G2-ES-SCO110', 'SCIENCE-G2-ES-ELO4', 'SCIENCE-G2-ES', 'SCIENCE', 'science', 'G2', '2', 'Earth Systems', 'Distinguish salt water and fresh water.', 1177, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:22.85096+00:00'),
  ('SCIENCE-G2-ES-SCO111', 'SCIENCE-G2-ES-ELO4', 'SCIENCE-G2-ES', 'SCIENCE', 'science', 'G2', '2', 'Earth Systems', 'Observe and describe the physical changes that occur when water freezes, melts, and evaporates.', 1178, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:22.85096+00:00'),
  ('SCIENCE-G2-ES-SCO112', 'SCIENCE-G2-ES-ELO4', 'SCIENCE-G2-ES', 'SCIENCE', 'science', 'G2', '2', 'Earth Systems', 'Observe and interpret a condensation experiment.', 1179, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:22.85096+00:00'),
  ('SCIENCE-G2-ES-SCO113', 'SCIENCE-G2-ES-ELO4', 'SCIENCE-G2-ES', 'SCIENCE', 'science', 'G2', '2', 'Earth Systems', 'Classify the various sources of water on earth as solid, liquid or gas.', 1180, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:22.85096+00:00'),
  ('SCIENCE-G2-ES-SCO114', 'SCIENCE-G2-ES-ELO4', 'SCIENCE-G2-ES', 'SCIENCE', 'science', 'G2', '2', 'Earth Systems', 'Show how a thermometer can measure the temperature.', 1181, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:22.85096+00:00'),
  ('SCIENCE-G2-ES-SCO115', 'SCIENCE-G2-ES-ELO4', 'SCIENCE-G2-ES', 'SCIENCE', 'science', 'G2', '2', 'Earth Systems', 'Measure the temperature of frozen water, water and boiling water.', 1182, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:22.85096+00:00'),
  ('SCIENCE-G2-ES-SCO117', 'SCIENCE-G2-ES-ELO4', 'SCIENCE-G2-ES', 'SCIENCE', 'science', 'G2', '2', 'Earth Systems', 'Use fists to demonstrate particle distance in solids, liquids and gas.', 1184, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:22.85096+00:00'),
  ('SCIENCE-G2-ES-SCO118', 'SCIENCE-G2-ES-ELO4', 'SCIENCE-G2-ES', 'SCIENCE', 'science', 'G2', '2', 'Earth Systems', 'Use fist model to explain the processes in the water cycle: (evaporation, condensation, precipitation). ', 1185, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:22.85096+00:00'),
  ('SCIENCE-G2-ES-SCO119', 'SCIENCE-G2-ES-ELO4', 'SCIENCE-G2-ES', 'SCIENCE', 'science', 'G2', '2', 'Earth Systems', 'Debate the importance of water conservation. ', 1186, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:22.85096+00:00'),
  ('SCIENCE-G2-ES-SCO120', 'SCIENCE-G2-ES-ELO4', 'SCIENCE-G2-ES', 'SCIENCE', 'science', 'G2', '2', 'Earth Systems', 'Apply the reuse, recycle and reduce model to community improvement. ', 1187, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:22.85096+00:00'),
  ('SCIENCE-G2-ES-SCO121', 'SCIENCE-G2-ES-ELO4', 'SCIENCE-G2-ES', 'SCIENCE', 'science', 'G2', '2', 'Earth Systems', 'Observe the evaporation and condensation of water (ST-3ESS-EW-6). ', 1188, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:22.85096+00:00'),
  ('SCIENCE-G2-ES-SCO122', 'SCIENCE-G2-ES-ELO4', 'SCIENCE-G2-ES', 'SCIENCE', 'science', 'G2', '2', 'Earth Systems', 'Collect and compare measurements of rainfall, temperature, wind direction and windspeed during a specific period (ST-2-ESS-EW-7). ', 1189, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:22.85096+00:00'),
  ('SCIENCE-G2-ES-SCO123', 'SCIENCE-G2-ES-ELO4', 'SCIENCE-G2-ES', 'SCIENCE', 'science', 'G2', '2', 'Earth Systems', 'Use a thermometer to measure temperature and, explain how the device works (ST-3-ESS-EW-9). ', 1190, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:22.85096+00:00'),
  ('SCIENCE-G2-ES-SCO124', 'SCIENCE-G2-ES-ELO4', 'SCIENCE-G2-ES', 'SCIENCE', 'science', 'G2', '2', 'Earth Systems', 'Appreciation: Students will develop an appreciation for the importance of water as a precious natural resource and recognize the need for conservation efforts. ', 1191, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:22.85096+00:00'),
  ('SCIENCE-G2-ES-SCO125', 'SCIENCE-G2-ES-ELO4', 'SCIENCE-G2-ES', 'SCIENCE', 'science', 'G2', '2', 'Earth Systems', 'Interest/Curiosity: Students will develop a deep interest and curiosity in the topic of water by exploring and investigating its properties, distribution, and importance to living things.', 1192, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:22.85096+00:00'),
  ('SCIENCE-G2-ES-SCO126', 'SCIENCE-G2-ES-ELO4', 'SCIENCE-G2-ES', 'SCIENCE', 'science', 'G2', '2', 'Earth Systems', 'Inventiveness: Students will use their creativity and inventiveness to develop and implement solutions to real-world water-related problems, such as water pollution, scarcity, and distribution.', 1193, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:22.85096+00:00'),
  ('SCIENCE-G2-ES-SCO127', 'SCIENCE-G2-ES-ELO4', 'SCIENCE-G2-ES', 'SCIENCE', 'science', 'G2', '2', 'Earth Systems', 'Active Participation: Students will participate actively in classroom discussions related to water, developing critical thinking and communication skills through classroom debates, discussions and presentations about water.', 1194, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:22.85096+00:00'),
  ('SCIENCE-G2-ES-SCO128', 'SCIENCE-G2-ES-ELO4', 'SCIENCE-G2-ES', 'SCIENCE', 'science', 'G2', '2', 'Earth Systems', 'When conducting practical and group work, display sensitivity and offer assistance to peers who may have physical or learning challenges.  ', 1195, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:22.85096+00:00'),
  ('SCIENCE-G2-ED-SCO1', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED-ELO1', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED', 'SCIENCE', 'science', 'G2', '2', 'Engineering Design', 'Define the terms: 
•	Technology
•	Engineering
•	Problem 
•	Solution 
•	Engineer 
•	Inventions 
•	Mechanical Engineer 
•	Electrical Engineer 
•	Industrial Engineer 
•	Civil Engineer 
•	Design Loop
•	Diagonal side
•	Ramp
•	Recycling 
•	Biomedical Engineers', 1196, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:22.85096+00:00'),
  ('SCIENCE-G2-ED-SCO2', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED-ELO1', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED', 'SCIENCE', 'science', 'G2', '2', 'Engineering Design', 'Distinguish technology as a problem-solving human adaptation and engineering as the tangible products (solutions) to that process.', 1197, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:22.85096+00:00'),
  ('SCIENCE-G2-ED-SCO3', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED-ELO1', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED', 'SCIENCE', 'science', 'G2', '2', 'Engineering Design', 'Demonstrate an understanding that engineers plan and design objects and tools  that are designed to solve problems faced by people.', 1198, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:22.85096+00:00'),
  ('SCIENCE-G2-ED-SCO4', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED-ELO1', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED', 'SCIENCE', 'science', 'G2', '2', 'Engineering Design', 'Show how people are affected by natural and human-made problems or situations which they want to be changed or solved. ', 1199, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:22.85096+00:00');
INSERT INTO curriculum_spine_scos (id, elo_id, strand_id, subject_id, subject_slug, grade_id, grade_level, strand_name, sco_text, sco_order, integrated_units, created_at) VALUES
  ('SCIENCE-G2-ED-SCO5', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED-ELO1', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED', 'SCIENCE', 'science', 'G2', '2', 'Engineering Design', 'Identify natural or human-made problems or situations to be changed or solved, in the home, school and community.', 1200, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:22.85096+00:00'),
  ('SCIENCE-G2-ED-SCO6', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED-ELO1', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED', 'SCIENCE', 'science', 'G2', '2', 'Engineering Design', 'Identify possible solutions to the problems based on observation and research (what others have done to solve similar problems).', 1201, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:22.85096+00:00'),
  ('SCIENCE-G2-ED-SCO7', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED-ELO1', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED', 'SCIENCE', 'science', 'G2', '2', 'Engineering Design', 'Describe the features of the tool or object that would solve a problem based on scientific information, materials used, and how it would be of benefit to people and the environment. ', 1202, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:22.85096+00:00'),
  ('SCIENCE-G2-ED-SCO8', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED-ELO1', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED', 'SCIENCE', 'science', 'G2', '2', 'Engineering Design', 'Explain in their own words, the interrelationship between Science and Technology (ST-2-TE-TM-3).', 1203, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:22.85096+00:00'),
  ('SCIENCE-G2-ED-SCO9', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED-ELO1', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED', 'SCIENCE', 'science', 'G2', '2', 'Engineering Design', 'Realise that some things are natural and some are human-made (ST2-TE-NT-1).', 1204, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:22.85096+00:00'),
  ('SCIENCE-G2-ED-SCO10', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED-ELO1', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED', 'SCIENCE', 'science', 'G2', '2', 'Engineering Design', 'Match simple gadgets to the use to which they were put (ST-2TE-TM-2).', 1205, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:22.85096+00:00'),
  ('SCIENCE-G2-ED-SCO11', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED-ELO1', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED', 'SCIENCE', 'science', 'G2', '2', 'Engineering Design', 'Identify and appreciate that the gadgets, tools and structures used in their homes and community are made by humans (ST-3-TE-UT-1).', 1206, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:22.85096+00:00'),
  ('SCIENCE-G2-ED-SCO12', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED-ELO1', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED', 'SCIENCE', 'science', 'G2', '2', 'Engineering Design', 'Demonstrate an understanding of a design approach by using the design loop or design steps in a real design challenge.', 1207, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:22.85096+00:00'),
  ('SCIENCE-G2-ED-SCO13', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED-ELO1', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED', 'SCIENCE', 'science', 'G2', '2', 'Engineering Design', 'Make predictions about how to solve a real design challenge.', 1208, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:22.85096+00:00'),
  ('SCIENCE-G2-ED-SCO14', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED-ELO1', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED', 'SCIENCE', 'science', 'G2', '2', 'Engineering Design', 'Make drawings of proposed solutions to real design challenges.', 1209, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:22.85096+00:00'),
  ('SCIENCE-G2-ED-SCO15', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED-ELO1', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED', 'SCIENCE', 'science', 'G2', '2', 'Engineering Design', 'Hypothesize why problem solutions worked or didn’t satisfy the design challenge.', 1210, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:22.85096+00:00'),
  ('SCIENCE-G2-ED-SCO16', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED-ELO1', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED', 'SCIENCE', 'science', 'G2', '2', 'Engineering Design', 'Develop manual dexterity in building a solution to a real design challenge.', 1211, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:22.85096+00:00'),
  ('SCIENCE-G2-ED-SCO17', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED-ELO1', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED', 'SCIENCE', 'science', 'G2', '2', 'Engineering Design', 'Making measurements and preparing a scaled drawing. ', 1212, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:22.85096+00:00'),
  ('SCIENCE-G2-ED-SCO18', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED-ELO1', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED', 'SCIENCE', 'science', 'G2', '2', 'Engineering Design', 'Predicting a materials list for a project. ', 1213, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:22.85096+00:00'),
  ('SCIENCE-G2-ED-SCO19', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED-ELO1', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED', 'SCIENCE', 'science', 'G2', '2', 'Engineering Design', 'Observe and record natural or human made problems or situations that are affecting people, in the home, school and community. ', 1214, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:22.85096+00:00'),
  ('SCIENCE-G2-ED-SCO20', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED-ELO1', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED', 'SCIENCE', 'science', 'G2', '2', 'Engineering Design', 'Construct a device or tool, based on the plan, to solve the problem. ', 1215, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:22.85096+00:00'),
  ('SCIENCE-G2-ED-SCO21', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED-ELO1', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED', 'SCIENCE', 'science', 'G2', '2', 'Engineering Design', 'Predict the possible outcomes/results or benefits of the designed tool. ', 1216, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:22.85096+00:00'),
  ('SCIENCE-G2-ED-SCO22', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED-ELO1', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED', 'SCIENCE', 'science', 'G2', '2', 'Engineering Design', 'Demonstrate the ability to explain to people the why/how and benefit of their model design.', 1217, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:22.85096+00:00'),
  ('SCIENCE-G2-ED-SCO23', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED-ELO1', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED', 'SCIENCE', 'science', 'G2', '2', 'Engineering Design', 'Given problems, be able to design and construct simple gadgets (ST-2-TE-TM-1).', 1218, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:22.85096+00:00'),
  ('SCIENCE-G2-ED-SCO24', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED-ELO1', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED', 'SCIENCE', 'science', 'G2', '2', 'Engineering Design', 'Evaluate two different gadgets using named criteria (ST-2-TETM-4).', 1219, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:22.85096+00:00'),
  ('SCIENCE-G2-ED-SCO25', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED-ELO1', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED', 'SCIENCE', 'science', 'G2', '2', 'Engineering Design', 'Share information with peers on the nature of technology (St-2TE-NT-2).', 1220, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:22.85096+00:00'),
  ('SCIENCE-G2-ED-SCO26', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED-ELO1', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED', 'SCIENCE', 'science', 'G2', '2', 'Engineering Design', 'Formulate problems and do research in development of technological devices (construct models and gadgets) (ST-3TE-TM-1) ', 1221, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:22.85096+00:00'),
  ('SCIENCE-G2-ED-SCO27', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED-ELO1', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED', 'SCIENCE', 'science', 'G2', '2', 'Engineering Design', 'Appreciate the importance of finding solutions to everyday problems and of objects and tools created/ used to solve problems.', 1222, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:22.85096+00:00'),
  ('SCIENCE-G2-ED-SCO28', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED-ELO1', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED', 'SCIENCE', 'science', 'G2', '2', 'Engineering Design', 'Understanding the importance of problem-solving as a life skill.', 1223, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:22.85096+00:00'),
  ('SCIENCE-G2-ED-SCO29', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED-ELO1', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED', 'SCIENCE', 'science', 'G2', '2', 'Engineering Design', 'Becoming aware of the viability and importance of careers in engineering and technology.', 1224, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:22.85096+00:00'),
  ('SCIENCE-G2-ED-SCO30', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED-ELO1', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED', 'SCIENCE', 'science', 'G2', '2', 'Engineering Design', 'Participate actively in classroom discussions, contributing design ideas.', 1225, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:22.85096+00:00'),
  ('SCIENCE-G2-ED-SCO31', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED-ELO1', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED', 'SCIENCE', 'science', 'G2', '2', 'Engineering Design', 'Collaborating productively in team preparation of design planning and construction of solutions. ', 1226, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:22.85096+00:00'),
  ('SCIENCE-G2-ED-SCO32', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED-ELO1', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED', 'SCIENCE', 'science', 'G2', '2', 'Engineering Design', 'Express the desire to find solutions to the problem identified by asking many questions during the survey to understand the problems faced by people. ', 1227, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:22.85096+00:00'),
  ('SCIENCE-G2-ED-SCO33', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED-ELO1', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED', 'SCIENCE', 'science', 'G2', '2', 'Engineering Design', 'Demonstrate an awareness of the need to care for the environment by recycling materials to construct a tool or object to solve the problem identified. ', 1228, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:22.85096+00:00'),
  ('SCIENCE-G2-ED-SCO34', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED-ELO1', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED', 'SCIENCE', 'science', 'G2', '2', 'Engineering Design', 'Show sensitivity and assist their peers who may have learning and physical challenges as they are engaged in the engineering design process. ', 1229, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:22.85096+00:00'),
  ('SCIENCE-G2-ED-SCO35', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED-ELO1', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED', 'SCIENCE', 'science', 'G2', '2', 'Engineering Design', 'Appreciate the advantages and disadvantages of using devices, tools and structures made by humans (ST-2TE-UT-1).', 1230, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:22.85096+00:00'),
  ('SCIENCE-G2-ED-SCO36', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED-ELO1', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED', 'SCIENCE', 'science', 'G2', '2', 'Engineering Design', 'Scientific and technological activities are usually influenced by the values and beliefs of humans and their societies.', 1231, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:22.85096+00:00'),
  ('SCIENCE-G2-ED-SCO37', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED-ELO2', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED', 'SCIENCE', 'science', 'G2', '2', 'Engineering Design', 'Define the terms:
•	Shape
•	Technology
•	Engineering
•	Problems
•	Solutions
•	Design Brief
•	Prototype
•	Disability
•	Biomedical engineers
•	Blunt/sharp nose
•	Lock/Key
•	Controlled Experiment', 1232, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:22.85096+00:00'),
  ('SCIENCE-G2-ED-SCO38', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED-ELO2', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED', 'SCIENCE', 'science', 'G2', '2', 'Engineering Design', 'Demonstrate an understanding that the shape of an object depends on its function to solve a given problem.', 1233, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:22.85096+00:00'),
  ('SCIENCE-G2-ED-SCO39', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED-ELO2', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED', 'SCIENCE', 'science', 'G2', '2', 'Engineering Design', 'Recognize that there are different designs for a roof and that some designs are better for resisting the effects of wind and rain.', 1234, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:22.85096+00:00'),
  ('SCIENCE-G2-ED-SCO40', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED-ELO2', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED', 'SCIENCE', 'science', 'G2', '2', 'Engineering Design', 'Identify objects in the school, house and community that have specific shapes based on their functions.', 1235, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:22.85096+00:00'),
  ('SCIENCE-G2-ED-SCO41', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED-ELO2', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED', 'SCIENCE', 'science', 'G2', '2', 'Engineering Design', 'Recognize that certain shapes are required in order for a designed object to solve the problem.', 1236, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:22.85096+00:00'),
  ('SCIENCE-G2-ED-SCO42', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED-ELO2', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED', 'SCIENCE', 'science', 'G2', '2', 'Engineering Design', 'Recognize that keys are very carefully prepared to exactly fit a lock and that this allows us to have secure homes and storage facilities. ', 1237, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:22.85096+00:00'),
  ('SCIENCE-G2-ED-SCO43', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED-ELO2', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED', 'SCIENCE', 'science', 'G2', '2', 'Engineering Design', ' Give examples of how poor design can lead to unsafe use and danger. ', 1238, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:22.85096+00:00'),
  ('SCIENCE-G2-ED-SCO44', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED-ELO2', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED', 'SCIENCE', 'science', 'G2', '2', 'Engineering Design', 'Be aware that there are engineers that assist humans with physical challenges and that this is an exciting and rewarding career. ', 1239, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:22.85096+00:00'),
  ('SCIENCE-G2-ED-SCO45', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED-ELO2', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED', 'SCIENCE', 'science', 'G2', '2', 'Engineering Design', 'Match simple gadgets to the use to which they are put (ST-2-TE-TM-2). ', 1240, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:22.85096+00:00'),
  ('SCIENCE-G2-ED-SCO46', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED-ELO2', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED', 'SCIENCE', 'science', 'G2', '2', 'Engineering Design', 'Identify and appreciate that the gadgets, tools and structures used in their homes and community are made by humans(ST-3-TE-UT-1).  ', 1241, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:22.85096+00:00'),
  ('SCIENCE-G2-ED-SCO47', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED-ELO2', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED', 'SCIENCE', 'science', 'G2', '2', 'Engineering Design', 'Understand and practice the engineering loop of stating the problem, creating a solution drawing and testing the prototype design. ', 1242, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:22.85096+00:00'),
  ('SCIENCE-G2-ED-SCO48', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED-ELO2', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED', 'SCIENCE', 'science', 'G2', '2', 'Engineering Design', 'Investigate how the shape of an object depends on its function to solve a given problem.', 1243, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:22.85096+00:00'),
  ('SCIENCE-G2-ED-SCO49', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED-ELO2', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED', 'SCIENCE', 'science', 'G2', '2', 'Engineering Design', 'Sketch or draw to simply illustrate how the shape of an object depends on its function to solve a given problem.', 1244, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:22.85096+00:00'),
  ('SCIENCE-G2-ED-SCO50', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED-ELO2', 'SCIENCE-G2-ED', 'SCIENCE', 'science', 'G2', '2', 'Engineering Design', 'Communicate effectively to explain their sketches or drawings as to how the shape of an object helps to solve a given problem.', 1245, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:22.85096+00:00'),
